extendedInfo.description: Play this super fun snake game as the Side/Winders band! Control Ryan, Lillard, Al, Kidd, and Casey as they seek out LOVE, BOOZE, and ROCK n' ROLL. The band members are the snake. The goal of the game is to grow, grow and grow. To grow, the Side/Winders need food. But this is a ROCKSTAR band and they ONLY thrive on HEARTBREAK, ALCOHOL and MUSIC.Be careful! The Side/Winders must always be moving.Help the SIDE/WINDERS reach Rockstardom! Check out their music and band at http://sidewindersmusic.comThis is a perfect bathroom game.
